<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٩٣٤ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">‌قُتَيْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1132">‌جَرِيرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">‌مَنْصُورٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">‌إِبْرَاهِيمَ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2343">‌وَسَعِيدِ بْنِ جُبَيْرٍ</a> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُمَا كَانَا لَا يَرَيَانِ بَأْسًا بِاسْتِئْجَارِ الْأَرْضِ الْبَيْضَاءِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>